---
import Picture from 'astro/components/Picture.astro'
import filepassImage from '../assets/images/filepass.png'
import whatIsProductionImage from '../assets/images/production_what-is-production.webp'
import whatYouCanExpectImage from '../assets/images/production_what-you-can-expect.webp'
import MainContent from '../components/MainContent.astro'
import TextContent from '../components/text/Content.astro'
import PageHeader from '../components/text/PageHeader.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Robby Webb | Production">
  <MainContent>
    <PageHeader class="page-header-custom" text="Production" />

    <section id="production" class="production">
      <article id="what-is-production">
        <Picture
          src={whatIsProductionImage}
          formats={['avif', 'webp']}
          alt="Robby Webb Production"
        />
        <TextContent alignment="right">
          <p>
            Music production is the canvas of sound, where every stroke, color, and texture come
            together to form a masterpiece. It encompasses the entire journey of a song from its
            initial idea to its final master. A producer is your guide, mentor, and collaborator,
            ensuring that each element of the song serves its purpose and contributes to the overall
            narrative.
          </p>
          <p>
            It's about shaping the song's architecture, choosing the right sounds, and creating an
            environment where artists can shine. The role of a producer is multifaceted, blending
            creativity with technical prowess to enhance the song's emotional depth and sonic
            quality.
          </p>
        </TextContent>
      </article>

      <article id="what-you-can-expect" class="aos-fade">
        <Picture
          src={whatYouCanExpectImage}
          formats={['avif', 'webp']}
          alt="Robby Webb producing"
        />
        <TextContent>
          <p>Here's what your production journey looks like with me:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Personalized Approach:</strong> Every artist is unique, and so is every song. We
              tailor our production process to fit your style, your goals, and your vision.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Creative Environment:</strong> We provide a space where creativity flows freely,
              where you're encouraged to explore, experiment, and express yourself musically.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Technical Mastery:</strong> Leveraging cutting-edge technology and time-honored
              techniques, we sculpt your music to sound pristine on every platform, from headphones to
              live stages.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Empowerment:</strong> Our goal is to empower you as an artist. We provide insights,
              techniques, and perspectives that enhance your musical expression and propel your career
              forward.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </TextContent>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="listen" class="listen aos-fade">
      <Picture src={filepassImage} formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Robby Webb producing" />
      <a href="/contact" class="site-cta large">Let's Get Started</a>
    </section>
  </MainContent>
</Layout>

<style>
  .production,
  .listen {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-section) + 4rem);
  }

  .production article {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-section) + 4rem);
    grid-template-areas:
      'image'
      'content';
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-section) + 4rem);

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      grid-template-areas: 'image content';
      gap: var(--spacing-section);

      &:nth-child(2) {
        grid-template-areas: 'content image';
      }
    }

    & img {
      grid-area: image;
      filter: brightness(0.8);
    }
  }

  .listen {
    max-width: var(--container-small-width);
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;

    & .site-cta {
      margin: var(--spacing-section) auto 0;
    }
  }
</style>
